{"slug":"sirkuler-23-550e-10962","reference":"Sirkuler_23_550E","gazette":"EU OJ L 148, 8.6.2023","title":"EU anti-dumping/countervailing duties on Chinese hot-rolled coil will remain in place for at least another 5 years","date":"12 Haziran 2023","bodyHtml":"<p>Tariffs on Chinese hot-rolled coil will remain in place for at least another 5 years.</p><p>The European Commission (EC) announced the extension of anti-dumping and countervailing duties on the import of certain types of hot-rolled flat products for another 5 years. SteelOrbis reports about it.</p><p>A request for a repeat anti-dumping investigation was submitted by the European Steel Association EUROFEER in 2022. The association indicated that the expiry of the measures on Chinese steel products is likely to result in the continuation or recurrence of dumping for the EU steel industry.<br></p><p>Anti-dumping duties range from 1% to 31.3%, and countervailing duties range from 4.6 to 35.9%.<br></p><p>The products to which tariffs are subject to the following types of goods according to the positions of customs statistics – 7208 10 00, 7208 25 00, 7208 26 00, 7208 27 00, 7208 36 00, 7208 37 00, 7208 38 00, 7208 3 9 00, 7208 40 00, 7208 52 10, 7208 52 99, 7208 53 10, 7208 53 90, 7208 54 00, 7211 13 00, 7211 14 00, 7211 19 00, ex 7225 19 10, 7225 30 90, ex 7225 40 60, 7225 40 90, ex 7226 19 10, 7226 91 91 та 7226 91 99.</p><p>The following products are not covered by the measures:</p><p>(i)  products of stainless steel and grain-oriented silicon electrical steel,</p><p>ii) products of tool steel and high-speed steel,</p><p>(iii) products, not in coils, without patterns in relief, of a thickness exceeding 10 mm and of a width of 600 mm or more, and</p><p>(iv) products, not in coils, without patterns in relief, of a thickness of 4,75 mm or more but not exceeding 10 mm and of a width of 2 050 mm or more.</p><p><a  href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=uriserv:OJ.L_.2023.148.01.0045.01.ENG&toc=OJ:L:2023:148:TOC\" target=\"_blank\" xss=removed>Please click for the anti dumping duty regulation..</a><br></p><p><a  href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=uriserv:OJ.L_.2023.148.01.0084.01.ENG&toc=OJ:L:2023:148:TOC\" target=\"_blank\" xss=removed>Please click for the Countervailing duty regulation.</a></p><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><colgroup><col width=\"22%\"><col width=\"26%\"><col width=\"30%\"><col width=\"22%\"></colgroup><tbody><tr class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-hdr\" xss=removed>Country</p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-hdr\" xss=removed>Company</p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-hdr\" xss=removed>Countervailing duty</p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-hdr\" xss=removed>TARIC additional code</p></td></tr><tr class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-txt\" xss=removed>People’s Republic of China</p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-txt\" xss=removed>Bengang Steel Plates Co., Ltd.</p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-num\" xss=removed>28,1  %</p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-txt\" xss=removed>C157</p></td></tr><tr class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-normal\" xss=removed> </p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-txt\" xss=removed>Handan Iron & Steel Group Han-Bao Co., Ltd.</p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-num\" xss=removed>7,8  %</p></td><td valign=\"top\" class=\"oj-table\" xss=removed><p class=\"oj-tbl-txt\" xss=removed>C158</p></td></tr><tr class=\"oj-table\" xss=rem